metadata.title: Rivers 1:2,000,000 - PWS, Copper Rivers
metadata.description: Data Type: Freshwater Systems;  This layer contains major river data for the Prince William Sound - Copper River ecosystem at 1:2,000,000 scale. Pacific GIS derived this layer from a statewide, Digital Line Graph (DLG) coverage  obtained from USGS.
